    "Since that time, the FDA has issued new guidance for regulatory oversight of clinical AI/ML.",
    "While regulatory oversight of health AI/ML is visibly improving, it can be argued that continuous improvements are always feasible and desirable as the technology and its implementation advances and expands.",
    "Chapter \"Regulatory Aspects and Ethical Legal Societal Implications (ELSI)\" delves into the details of the regulatory landscape and criteria.",
    "Selected Case Studies of Problems with Commercial or Commercially-Promoted Health AI/ML TechnologyWe provide here a small selection of case studies involving commercial health AI/ ML.",
